Description
-----------

This CVar sets which side of point lights should be drawn for shadow
buffer.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_sb_singleside [Int]

Parameters
----------

-   [Int]
    -   -1 - Draw all.
    -   0 - Draw side 0.
    -   1 - Draw side 1.
    -   2 - Draw side 2.
    -   3 - Draw side 3.
    -   4 - Draw side 4.
    -   5 - Draw side 5.

